        "product_description": {
            "value": "Bring a splash of adventure to hydration with this Paw Patrol 15.5oz Stainless Steel Vector Bottle by Zak Designs. Featuring your favorite rescue pups, this durable stainless steel water bottle is perfect for kids on the go, whether heading to school, sports practice, or a day of outdoor fun. The convenient push button spout opens with a single press for easy, one-handed sipping, while the attached carry loop makes it simple to clip onto backpacks or grab on the way out the door. Built to withstand daily use, the sturdy stainless steel construction helps keep beverages cool and resists dents and wear. The colorful, kid-friendly Paw Patrol graphics add personality and make this bottle a favorite for young fans. With a generous 15.5oz capacity, it holds plenty of water to keep children refreshed throughout their busy day. Ideal for lunchboxes, picnics, and travel, this reusable bottle is an eco-friendly alternative to disposable options. Hand washing is recommended to preserve the vibrant designs and ensure long-lasting use.",
